icket id, category, subject, and status. I am working on how to integrate the dynamic SLA timer and status display within the ticket's row element.\n\n\n**Developing Ticket Display**\n\nI am now focusing on the single-ticket view. I'm prioritizing integrating the display with the provided JSX code, structuring the layout for data presentation. Currently, I am structuring and organizing the ticket details, including ticket ID, client, and subject. I am also planning on rendering the close button.\n\n\n**Refining Event Handling**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on event handling within the table rows, specifically within the given sample code. I am focusing on making the click and keypress actions more efficient, and preventing unintended behavior. I am also working on improving event propagation. I plan on handling the copy ID functionality to improve event management and responsiveness.\n\n\n**Implementing Copy Functionality**\n\nI am now focusing on the copy ID button within each ticket row. My goal is to integrate a confirmation visual indicator for successful copies. I am working to refine the click handler to update the button's appearance immediately after the copy action. Currently I am refining the visual feedback, integrating a checkmark icon to confirm.\n\n\n**Rendering Status & Icons**\n\nI'm now focusing on integrating the status display and conditional icon rendering within the ticket row. Specifically, I am refining the dynamic status rendering using the `getStatusStyles` function. I am now working on determining the best way to determine the use case for the given icons. I'm prioritizing clarity for the display.\n\n\n**Integrating Mobile Responsiveness**\n\nI'm now focusing on integrating mobile responsiveness into the ticket display, and specifically, the given JSX code. I am working on using the grid layout to refactor the ticket display to accommodate smaller screens. I am also working to ensure that the layout remains clear and usable on mobile devices.\n\n\n**Developing Ticket Display Refinement**\n\nI'm now integrating the JSX block for a single ticket into the larger display. Currently, I'm focusing on rendering ticket details, including ID, subject, and client, within the given format. The goal is a clear and concise presentation, with appropriate styling to match the established design. My focus is now on integrating the other data.\n\n\n**Structuring Ticket Display**\n\nI am now structuring the single ticket display. I'm focusing on the integration of a close button. I am concentrating on arranging ticket details, including ID, subject, and client. I am currently evaluating the close button's positioning and action. I'm working to refine this view, making sure it maintains clarity.\n\n\n**Visualizing Telemetry Flow**\n\nI'm now diving into the styling for a new visual component. I'm focusing on the animation of the flow particles within the \"Enclave Telemetry Bridge\". I'm currently using keyframes to control the animation, including `flowParticle` to refine the visual effect. I'm focusing on stroke-dasharray to control the motion.\n\n\n**Animating Status Indicators**\n\nI'm now focusing on visually representing the ticket status within the single ticket view. I'm exploring the dynamic rendering of both the circular indicator and the corresponding text. The current emphasis is on integrating the status styles and animations. I'm incorporating the conditional logic for various ticket states.\n\n\n**Refining Node Visualization**\n\nI'm now refining the visualization of nodes and flow paths, focusing on integrating conditional styling based on ticket status and priority. I'm dynamically adjusting stroke colors and animation classes to reflect these states. Currently, I'm focusing on the \"Client Node\" and its visual representation within the existing JSX structure.\n\n\n\n**Visualizing Agent Indicators**\n\nI'm now focusing on conditionally rendering indicators within the existing SVG structure. I'm dynamically updating the visualization for the Admin Node. I'm focusing on the assigned agent and ticket status attributes, specifically to ensure that the visual indicators accurately reflect the assigned agent and the status.\n\n\n\n**Visualizing Security States**\n\nI'm now focusing on integrating the security state indicators, specifically within the existing SVG structure. I'm dynamically updating the text and rectangle components. Currently, I am focused on the \"ATTESTATION_OFF\" and \"TLS_1.3_SECURE\" states, and their respective visual representations.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T07:47:26.230Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"bnkxfhji","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/admin/support/page.tsx","old_text":"          <tbody>\n            {filteredTickets.map((t) => (\n              <tr \n                key={t.id}\n                onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(t.id)}\n                className={`border-b border-white/[0.02] last:border-0 hover:bg-white/[0.01] cursor-pointer transition-colors ${selectedTicketId === t.id ? \"bg-white/[0.02]\" : \"\"}`}\n              >\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4 font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1\">\n                    <span>{t.id}</span>\n                    <button onClick={(e) => handleCopyId(e, t.id)} className=\"opacity-40 hover:opacity-100 p-0.5\" title=\"Copy ID\">\n                      {copiedTicketId === t.id ? <Check className=\"w-3 h-3 text-emerald-400\" /> : <Copy className=\"w-3 h-3\" />}\n                    </button>\n                  </div>\n                </td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white font-semibold block truncate max-w-[250px]\">{t.subject}</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white/30 text-[9.5px] block uppercase\">{t.client.split(\" [\")[0]}</span>\n                  </div>\n                </td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4\">\n                  <span className={`inline-flex px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border text-[9px] font-bold ${t.priority === \"P1\" ? \"text-red-400 border-red-500/20 bg-red-500/5\" : \"text-amber-400 border-amber-500/20 bg-amber-500/5\"}`}>{t.priority} SLA</span>\n                </td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4 text-white/70\">{t.category.toUpperCase()}</td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4\">\n                  <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1\">\n                    <span className={`w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full ${t.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"bg-emerald-500\" : \"bg-amber-400 animate-pulse\"}`} />\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase\">{t.status}</span>\n                  </span>\n                </td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4 text-white/80\">{t.assignedAgent}</td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4\">\n                  <div className=\"flex gap-1.5 text-white/40\">\n                    {t.linkedProjectId !== \"None\" && <Folder className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />}\n                    {t.linkedDocId !== \"None\" && <FileText className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400\" />}\n                  </div>\n                </td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4 text-right font-bold\">\n                  <span className={t.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"text-emerald-400\" : t.slaSeconds <= 0 ? \"text-red-500 font-extrabold animate-pulse\" : \"text-amber-400\"}>\n                    {formatSla(t.slaSeconds, t.status)}\n                  </span>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            ))}\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:hidden\">\n        {filteredTickets.map((t) => (\n          <div key={t.id} onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(t.id)} className={`border rounded-xl p-4 space-y-3 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm cursor-pointer ${selectedTicketId === t.id ? \"border-[#009DFF]\" : \"border-white/5\"}`}>\n            <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n              <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold font-mono text-[11px]\">{t.id}</span>\n              <span className=\"text-white/40 font-mono text-[9px] uppercase\">{t.category}</span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-white font-semibold text-xs leading-snug\">{t.subject}</h4>\n            <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-2 border-t border-white/5 font-mono text-[10px] text-white/50\">\n              <span>SLA TIMER:</span>\n              <span className={t.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"text-emerald-400 font-bold\" : \"text-amber-400 font-bold\"}>{formatSla(t.slaSeconds, t.status)}</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        ))}\n      </div>\n\n      {selectedTicket && (\n        <>\n          <div onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(null)} className=\"fixed inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm z-40 transition-all\" />\n          <div className=\"fixed inset-y-0 right-0 z-50 w-full sm:w-[500px] md:w-[600px] bg-[#070708] border-l border-white/10 shadow-2xl p-6 overflow-y-auto flex flex-col justify-between\">\n            <div className=\"space-y-5\">\n              <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold\">{selectedTicket.id}</span>\n                  <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white mt-2 leading-snug\">{selectedTicket.subject}</h3>\n                  <p className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase mt-1\">CLIENT: {selectedTicket.client}</p>\n                </div>\n                <button onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(null)} className=\"p-1 hover:bg-white/5 rounded text-white/40 cursor-pointer\"><X className=\"w-5 h-5\" /></button>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"flex border-b border-white/5 font-mono text-[9.5px] select-none\">","new_text":"          <tbody>\n            {filteredTickets.map((t) => (\n              <tr \n                key={t.id}\n                onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(t.id)}\n                onKeyDown={(e) => {\n                  if (e.key === \"Enter\" || e.key === \" \") {\n                    e.preventDefault();\n                    setSelectedTicketId(t.id);\n                  }\n                }}\n                tabIndex={0}\n                role=\"button\"\n                aria-pressed={selectedTicketId === t.id}\n                className={`border-b border-white/[0.02] last:border-0 hover:bg-white/[0.02] focus:bg-white/[0.03] outline-none cursor-pointer transition-colors ${selectedTicketId === t.id ? \"bg-white/[0.02]\" : \"\"}`}\n              >\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4 font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                    <span>{t.id}</span>\n                    <button \n                      onClick={(e) => handleCopyId(e, t.id)} \n                      className=\"opacity-40 hover:opacity-100 p-0.5 focus:opacity-100 outline-none rounded hover:bg-white/5\" \n                      title=\"Copy SLA Wire ID\"\n                    >\n                      {copiedTicketId === t.id ? <Check className=\"w-3 h-3 text-emerald-400\" /> : <Copy className=\"w-3 h-3\" />}\n                    </button>\n                  </div>\n                </td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white font-semibold block truncate max-w-[250px]\">{t.subject}</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white/30 text-[9.5px] block uppercase\">{t.client.split(\" [\")[0]}</span>\n                  </div>\n                </td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4\">\n                  <span className={`inline-flex px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border text-[9px] font-bold ${getPriorityBadgeStyles(t.priority)}`}>\n                    {t.priority} SLA\n                  </span>\n                </td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4 text-white/70\">{t.category.toUpperCase()}</td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4\">\n                  {(() => {\n                    const styles = getStatusStyles(t.status);\n                    return (\n                      <span className={`inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border text-[9px] font-bold ${styles.bgClass} ${styles.textClass}`}>\n                        <span className={`w-1 h-1 rounded-full ${styles.dotClass}`} />\n                        <span>{t.status}</span>\n                      </span>\n                    );\n                  })()}\n                </td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4 text-white/80\">{t.assignedAgent}</td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4\">\n                  <div className=\"flex gap-1.5 text-white/40\">\n                    {t.linkedProjectId !== \"None\" && <Folder className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2]\" title=\"Linked Project\" />}\n                    {t.linkedDocId !== \"None\" && <FileText className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400\" title=\"Linked Document\" />}\n                  </div>\n                </td>\n                <td className=\"py-3 px-4 text-right font-bold\">\n                  {renderSlaBadge(t)}\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            ))}\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:hidden\">\n        {filteredTickets.map((t) => (\n          <div \n            key={t.id} \n            onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(t.id)} \n            onKeyDown={(e) => {\n              if (e.key === \"Enter\" || e.key === \" \") {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                setSelectedTicketId(t.id);\n              }\n            }}\n            tabIndex={0}\n            role=\"button\"\n            aria-pressed={selectedTicketId === t.id}\n            className={`border rounded-xl p-4 space-y-3 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm cursor-pointer hover:bg-[#050505]/60 focus:border-[#009DFF] outline-none transition-all ${selectedTicketId === t.id ? \"border-[#009DFF]\" : \"border-white/5\"}`}\n          >\n            <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n              <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold font-mono text-[11px]\">{t.id}</span>\n              <span className={`inline-flex px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border text-[8px] font-bold ${getPriorityBadgeStyles(t.priority)}`}>\n                {t.priority}\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-white font-semibold text-xs leading-snug\">{t.subject}</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase mt-1\">{t.client.split(\" [\")[0]}</p>\n            <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-2 border-t border-white/5 font-mono text-[10px]\">\n              <span className=\"text-white/40 uppercase\">STATUS: {t.status}</span>\n              <span>{renderSlaBadge(t)}</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        ))}\n      </div>\n\n      {selectedTicket && (\n        <>\n          <div onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(null)} className=\"fixed inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm z-40 transition-all\" />\n          <div className=\"fixed inset-y-0 right-0 z-50 w-full sm:w-[500px] md:w-[600px] bg-[#070708] border-l border-white/10 shadow-2xl p-6 overflow-y-auto flex flex-col justify-between\">\n            <div className=\"space-y-5\">\n              <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold\">{selectedTicket.id}</span>\n                  <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white mt-2 leading-snug\">{selectedTicket.subject}</h3>\n                  <p className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase mt-1\">CLIENT: {selectedTicket.client}</p>\n                </div>\n                <button onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(null)} className=\"p-1 hover:bg-white/5 rounded text-white/40 cursor-pointer\"><X className=\"w-5 h-5\" /></button>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Secure Enclave Diagnostics Bridge Visualizer */}\n              <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-black/40 p-4 font-mono text-[10px] space-y-3 relative overflow-hidden\">\n                <style>{`\n                  @keyframes flowParticle {\n                    to { stroke-dashoffset: -20; }\n                  }\n                  .animate-flow-fast {\n                    stroke-dasharray: 6, 6;\n                    animation: flowParticle 0.6s linear infinite;\n                  }\n                  .animate-flow-normal {\n                    stroke-dasharray: 6, 6;\n                    animation: flowParticle 1.5s linear infinite;\n                  }\n                  .animate-flow-slow {\n                    stroke-dasharray: 6, 6;\n                    animation: flowParticle 3.5s linear infinite;\n                  }\n                `}</style>\n                \n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[8.5px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                  <span>Enclave Telemetry Bridge</span>\n                  <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1\">\n                    <span className={`w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full ${selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"bg-white/20\" : selectedTicket.priority === \"P1\" ? \"bg-red-500 animate-ping\" : \"bg-cyan-400 animate-pulse\"}`} />\n                    <span className={selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"text-white/40\" : selectedTicket.priority === \"P1\" ? \"text-red-400 font-bold\" : \"text-cyan-400\"}>\n                      {selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"TERMINATED\" : `${selectedTicket.priority} STREAM ACTIVE`}\n                    </span>\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"relative h-20 w-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n                  <svg className=\"w-full h-full overflow-visible\" viewBox=\"0 0 400 80\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                    {/* Background Arc */}\n                    <path d=\"M 40 40 Q 200 10 360 40\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.05)\" strokeWidth=\"3\" strokeLinecap=\"round\" />\n                    \n                    {/* Flow Arc */}\n                    {selectedTicket.status !== \"RESOLVED\" && (\n                      <path \n                        d=\"M 40 40 Q 200 10 360 40\" \n                        stroke={selectedTicket.status === \"HOLD\" ? \"#FBBF24\" : selectedTicket.priority === \"P1\" ? \"#F87171\" : \"#22D3EE\"} \n                        strokeWidth=\"1.5\" \n                        strokeLinecap=\"round\"\n                        className={selectedTicket.status === \"HOLD\" ? \"animate-flow-slow\" : selectedTicket.priority === \"P1\" ? \"animate-flow-fast\" : \"animate-flow-normal\"}\n                      />\n                    )}\n\n                    {/* Nodes */}\n                    {/* Client Node */}\n                    <g transform=\"translate(40, 40)\">\n                      <circle r=\"12\" fill=\"#070708\" stroke={selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\" : selectedTicket.priority === \"P1\" ? \"#EF4444\" : \"#06B6D4\"} strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n                      <circle r=\"6\" fill={selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" : selectedTicket.priority === \"P1\" ? \"#EF4444\" : \"#06B6D4\"} className={selectedTicket.status !== \"RESOLVED\" ? \"animate-pulse\" : \"\"} />\n                      {/* Pulse ring for warning */}\n                      {selectedTicket.status !== \"RESOLVED\" && selectedTicket.priority === \"P1\" && (\n                        <circle r=\"18\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" strokeWidth=\"1\" className=\"animate-ping opacity-30\" />\n                      )}\n                    </g>\n\n                    {/* Admin Node */}\n                    <g transform=\"translate(360, 40)\">\n                      <circle r=\"12\" fill=\"#070708\" stroke={selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\" : selectedTicket.assignedAgent === \"Unassigned\" ? \"#F59E0B\" : \"#10B981\"} strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n                      <circle r=\"6\" fill={selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" : selectedTicket.assignedAgent === \"Unassigned\" ? \"#F59E0B\" : \"#10B981\"} />\n                    </g>\n\n                    {/* Label tags inside SVG */}\n                    <text x=\"40\" y=\"68\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" fontSize=\"7\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">ENCLAVE</text>\n                    <text x=\"360\" y=\"68\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" fontSize=\"7\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\">TERMINAL</text>\n                    \n                    {/* Bridge attestation status */}\n                    <rect x=\"150\" y=\"28\" width=\"100\" height=\"14\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#070708\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\" />\n                    <text x=\"200\" y=\"37\" fill={selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" : \"#00FFC2\"} fontSize=\"6.5\" fontFamily=\"monospace\" textAnchor=\"middle\" fontWeight=\"bold\">\n                      {selectedTicket.status === \"RESOLVED\" ? \"ATTESTATION_OFF\" : \"TLS_1.3_SECURE\"}\n                    </text>\n                  </svg>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 pt-1 border-t border-white/5 text-[9px] text-white/50\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                    <div>CLIENT ENDPOINT: <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{selectedTicket.client.split(\" [\")[0]}</span></div>\n                    <div>SEALING ENGINE: <span className=\"text-white font-mono font-bold\">Intel SGX v2</span></div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1 text-right\">\n                    <div>OPERATIONAL NODE: <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{selectedTicket.id}-GATEWAY</span></div>\n                    <div>TUNNEL LATENCY: <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\">{selectedTicket.priority === \"P1\" ? \"145ms (HIGH)\" : \"42ms (NOMINAL)\"}</span></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"flex border-b border-white/5 font-mono text-[9.5px] select-none\">"}}}
