nd \"TERMINAL\" labels and the conditional text \"ATTESTATION_OFF\" or \"TLS_1.3_SECURE\". I see an opportunity to replace the first two with shorter alternatives. I'm also planning to shorten the other text by shortening the `if` and `else` conditions, which should reduce the overall character count.\n\n\n"}}
